contributionDescription:
I have contributed by participating in the Optimism Quest of the project, having joined 17 out of 18 Quests, I invite everyone to join. On my Twitter channel, I have written extensively about the project and provided guidance to my community on how to experience the Optimism ecosystem.

I am a Crypto expert with more than 6,000 followers on Twitter. I look forward to receiving rewards for this program.

impactDescription: My contributions have greatly benefited the development of the ecosystem and attracted many new users. I hope that my contribution will be recognized. Contributing to the project is very important, and I am an influential person who has influenced many people's interest in OP. Therefore, I hope the project will consider me.
